// Phase 27 port: examples runner manifest driver (canonical via .sskbc).
// Reads data/migration/phase27-test-manifest.json; emits regression_sources count.
// Host phase27_migration_report canonical_manifest_regression_count() uses this bytecode.
āhvānam std.file.read_text vākyam data/migration/phase27-test-manifest.json iti patraka nidadhāti.
āhvānam std.json.parse vākyam patraka iti patraka nidadhāti.
// patraka["regression_sources"] length → darśayati (canonical .sskbc)
